OL,3,CBurnham to propose 'a No 10 in the
OL,4,CNorth' in major speech
OL,6,FLabour leadership frontrunner Andy
OL,7,FBurnham will use a major speech to
OL,8,Fconfirm plans for a "No 10" in the
OL,9,FNorth, as he sets out his vision for
OL,10,Fdevolution and economic reform.
OL,12,FSpeaking in Manchester on Monday, the
OL,13,Fnewly elected Makerfield MP is
OL,14,Fexpected to pledge a "circuit-breaker"
OL,15,Ffor Britain and promise "good growth
OL,16,Fin every postcode", with allies
OL,17,Fbilling it as the biggest shift of
OL,18,Fpower from Whitehall in modern times.
OL,26,@pD@UOUpD@[O]vD@VOUvD@fO]wD@YOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
