OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782689571
OL,3,CBurnham to propose 'a No 10 in the
OL,4,CNorth' in major speech
OL,6,FThe former metro mayor will call for
OL,7,Fdecision-making to be pushed back into
OL,8,Flocal communities as part of his
OL,9,Fvision to "lift Britain back up".
OL,11,FBurnham, who served as a minister and
OL,12,Fon the Opposition frontbench before
OL,13,Fbecoming a regional mayor in 2017,
OL,14,Fwill argue his generation of
OL,15,Fpoliticians must take responsibility
OL,16,Ffor declining public trust.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782689571
OL,3,CBurnham to propose 'a No 10 in the
OL,4,CNorth' in major speech
OL,6,FHe is expected to commit to reforming
OL,7,Fpublic procurement, which will centre
OL,8,Fon "buying British" to revive industry
OL,9,Fand secure more "social value" through
OL,10,Fwork placements and apprenticeships.
OL,12,FEducation reforms will also be
OL,13,Funveiled, aimed at delivering what his
OL,14,Fteam describe as "true parity" between
OL,15,Facademic and technical routes.
OL,26,@pD@DOUpD@SO]qD@QOUqD@^O]vD@ROUvD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
