PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782689571
OL,3,CBurnham to propose 'a No 10 in the
OL,4,CNorth' in major speech
OL,6,FA long-standing proponent of
OL,7,Fdevolution, Burnham will set out plans
OL,8,Fto boost economic growth by giving
OL,9,Fregional mayors more control over
OL,10,Fsocial housing, welfare and post-16
OL,11,Feducation, according to The Times.
OL,13,FSuch an agenda would be in line with
OL,14,Fthe views he set out in his book, Head
OL,15,FNorth, alongside his friend and fellow
OL,16,Fmayor Steve Rotheram.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
