PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782689571
OL,3,CBurnham to propose 'a No 10 in the
OL,4,CNorth' in major speech
OL,6,FIn the book, Burnham said the current
OL,7,Fsystem saw regional leaders going "on
OL,8,Fbended knee" to Westminster and called
OL,9,Ffor a "more balanced approach, where
OL,10,Fcouncils and mayors were dealt some
OL,11,Fcards too".
OL,13,FBurnham is also expected to announce
OL,14,Fplans to move part of his prime
OL,15,Fministerial operation to the North of
OL,16,FEngland as part of efforts to push
OL,17,Fpower out of Whitehall and into the
OL,18,Fregions with a "No 10 North."
OL,26,@oD@cOUpD@LO]qD@GOUsD@JO]zD@POUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
