PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782689571
OL,3,CBurnham to propose 'a No 10 in the
OL,4,CNorth' in major speech
OL,6,FDeputy Labour leader Lucy Powell said
OL,7,Fthe newly-elected MP had built up a
OL,8,F"clear sense of purpose" and insisted
OL,9,Fpeople wanted the party to "get on
OL,10,Fwith the job" of governing.
OL,12,FBurnham defied national trends to
OL,13,Fincrease Labour's vote share in the
OL,14,FMakerfield by-election this month
OL,15,Ffollowing its disastrous set of local
OL,16,Felection results in May, which
OL,17,Fintensified calls for Starmer to go.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@XO]qD@\OUrD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
