FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782689571
OL,3,CBurnham to propose 'a No 10 in the
OL,4,CNorth' in major speech
OL,6,FBut the party has consistently slumped
OL,7,Fin the polls for months, and political
OL,8,Fopponents have called for a general
OL,9,Felection to come with the change in
OL,10,Fleader as speculation mounts about his
OL,11,Fpolicy platform.
OL,13,FReform UK, which made sweeping gains
OL,14,Fin May's local elections, has called
OL,15,Ffor a general election following Sir
OL,16,FKeir's resignation, while the Tories
OL,17,Fhave said they would be ready to fight
OL,18,Fone if needed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
