CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782689571
OL,3,CBurnham to propose 'a No 10 in the
OL,4,CNorth' in major speech
OL,6,FConservative Party chairman Kevin
OL,7,FHollinrake MP dismissed Mr Burnham's
OL,8,Fplans as "the politics of distraction".
OL,10,F"Andy Burnham's big idea is to shuffle
OL,11,Fpower between politicians. Not fix the
OL,12,Fwelfare system," he said.
OL,14,F"Not cut the taxes strangling working
OL,15,Ffamilies and British business. Not
OL,16,Ffund the defence our country
OL,17,Fdesperately needs.
OL,26,@pD@JOUpD@fO]rD@AOUtD@PO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
