FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782689571
OL,3,CBurnham to propose 'a No 10 in the
OL,4,CNorth' in major speech
OL,6,F"Just more devolution, more
OL,7,Fcommittees, more process. It's the
OL,8,Fpolitics of distraction from a Labour
OL,9,FParty that is deliberately avoiding
OL,10,Fthe questions that actually matter".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@cO]
